001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonCreator;
004import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
005import org.bitcoinj.base.Address;
006import org.bitcoinj.base.Coin;
007import org.bitcoinj.base.Sha256Hash;
008import org.bitcoinj.script.Script;
009import org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.conversion.HexUtil;
010
011/**
012 * Data class for UnspentOutput as returned by listUnspent RPC
013 * Because the class is immutable we have to give Jackson some hints via annotations.
014 */
015public class UnspentOutput implements UtxoInfo {
016    private final Sha256Hash  txid;
017    private final int         vout;
018    private final Address     address;
019    private final String      label;
020    private final Script      scriptPubKey;
021    private final Coin        amount;
022    private final int         confirmations;
023
024
025    private final String      redeemScript;
026    private final String      witnessScript;
027    private final boolean     spendable;
028    private final boolean     solvable;
029    private final String      desc;
030    private final boolean     safe;
031
032    @JsonCreator
033    public UnspentOutput(@JsonProperty("txid")          Sha256Hash  txid,
034                         @JsonProperty("vout")          int         vout,
035                         @JsonProperty("address")       Address     address,
036                         @JsonProperty("label")         String      label,
037                         @JsonProperty("scriptPubKey")  String      scriptPubKey,
038                         @JsonProperty("amount")        Coin        amount,
039                         @JsonProperty("confirmations") int         confirmations,
040                         @JsonProperty("redeemScript")  String      redeemScript,
041                         @JsonProperty("witnessScript") String      witnessScript,
042                         @JsonProperty("spendable")     boolean     spendable,
043                         @JsonProperty("solvable")      boolean     solvable,
044                         @JsonProperty("desc")          String      desc,
045                         @JsonProperty("safe")          boolean     safe) {
046        this.txid = txid;
047        this.vout = vout;
048        this.address = address;
049        this.label = label;
050        this.scriptPubKey = Script.parse(HexUtil.hexStringToByteArray(scriptPubKey));
051        this.amount = amount;
052        this.confirmations = confirmations;
053        this.redeemScript = redeemScript;
054        this.witnessScript = witnessScript;
055        this.spendable = spendable;
056        this.solvable = solvable;
057        this.desc = desc;
058        this.safe = safe;
059    }
060
061    public Sha256Hash getTxid() {
062        return txid;
063    }
064
065    public int getVout() {
066        return vout;
067    }
068
069    public Address getAddress() {
070        return address;
071    }
072
073    public String getLabel() {
074        return label;
075    }
076
077    public Script getScriptPubKey() {
078        return scriptPubKey;
079    }
080
081    public Coin getAmount() {
082        return amount;
083    }
084
085    public int getConfirmations() {
086        return confirmations;
087    }
088
089    public String getRedeemScript() {
090        return redeemScript;
091    }
092
093    public String getWitnessScript() {
094        return witnessScript;
095    }
096
097    public boolean isSpendable() {
098        return spendable;
099    }
100
101    public boolean isSolvable() {
102        return solvable;
103    }
104
105    public String getDesc() {
106        return desc;
107    }
108
109    public boolean isSafe() {
110        return safe;
111    }
112}
